CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 18, 1958, pg. A11 reads: "Dr. Gragg Speaks - Dr. Rose S. Gragg (standing in center) is surrounded by other program participants at the afternoon Women's Day program at Bethlehem Baptist Church, McKeesport, last Sunday. Seated, left to right, are: Mmes. Gladys McNairy, Ellis Blockson, George W.  White, Mary Alexander, Pauline Young, Paul Dippolito, J. Harold Hayes, Walter Lundberg and Sadie Carter.  Standing far right is Mrs. Georgia Pettiford, one of the ushers, and Mrs. Hazel Garland, mistress of ceremonies...- Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Gladys McNairy, Ellis Blockson, Mrs. George W.  White, Mary Alexander, guest speaker Dr. Rose S. Gregg, Pauline Young, Mrs. Paul Dippolito, Mrs. J. Harold Hayes, Mrs. Walter Lundberg, Sadie Carter, with Georgia Pettiford and Hazel Garland standing in background, at banquet table in Bethlehem Baptist Church for Women's Day program, McKeesport
